data.description: Step into a thoughtfully designed interior featuring three spacious bedrooms and three bathrooms. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a welcoming atmosphere for daily living and entertaining. The kitchen, the heart of the home, is updated with modern amenities and a layout that effortlessly caters to your every need. The countertops in the kitchen are updated with quartz. Upstairs, the three bathrooms provide convenience, with a bathroom adjoining each one to ensure that the morning routine is seamless and enjoyable. The newer carpet elevates the comfort as well. But the natural allure lies just beyond the back door—a sizeable backyard that invites you to bask in the beauty of nature; this backyard opens up to the beautiful Valley Hi golf course.
